                <head>12. Minutes of a Review Group Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d12fn1"
                        >Source: National Archives, Nixon Presidential Materials, <gloss
                            target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Files, <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss>
                        Institutional Files (<gloss target="#t_H1">H</gloss>-Files), Box <gloss
                            target="#t_H1">H</gloss>–111, <gloss target="#t_SRG1">SRG</gloss>
                        Minutes, Originals, 1969. Top Secret. The meeting took place in the
                        Situation Room at the White House. The full text of the minutes and
                        documentation related to <gloss target="#t_NSSM1">NSSM</gloss> 3 are printed
                        in <ref target="frus1969-76v34#d32">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1969–1976, volume XXXIV,
